Interface IPlugin

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    APFPlugin
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BukkitPlugin, BungeePlugin, SpongePlugin, VelocityPlugin

    public interface IPlugin
    Main interface all APF plugins implement.
